# Task Plugins

<%= partial 'includes/shared/extension-info.md.erb', locals: { extension_name: 'task', extension_version: '1.0', gocd_version: '15.1.0'} %>

The Task extension endpoint allows plugin authors to extend GoCD to run new tasks in addition to the defaults that GoCD provides.

If you're looking to start away with a basic template for task plugins, we recommend forking this [github repository](https://github.com/gocd-contrib/task-skeleton-plugin).
